<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.261198>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Preseved specimens, dorsal view. A, Megalobrachium mortenseni Haig, 1962, ovigerous female (MZUSP- 24529); B, Megalobrachium roseum (Rathbun, 1900), female (MZUSP- 19905); C, Megalobrachium soriatum (Say, 1818), male (MZUSP- 19903); D, Minyocerus angustus (Dana, 1852), ovigerous female (MZUSP- 17473); E, Pachycheles ackleianus A. Milne-Edwards, 1880, male (MZUSP- 19548); F, Pachycheles chubutensis Boschi, 1963, male (MZUSP- 7194); G, Pachycheles greeleyi (Rathbun, 1900), male (MZUSP- 21232); H, Pachycheles laevidactylus Ortmann, 1892, male (MZUSP- 18723). Scales: A – E (1 mm); F – H (5 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/261198/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

